<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stand-vi">stand <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stænd/    美 /stænd/  </p>
<p>(stood, stood)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>站立；起立：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>stand in a queue / stand in line
排队</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>stand in the way
挡道；阻挡</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>位于 (某处)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Here once stood an old castle.
以前这里有座古城堡。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The city stands on the bank of the Changjiang River
这座城市位于长江沿岸。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[用作系动词] 高度为；[不用于进行时] 达到...数量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are two buildings, the larger of which stands nearly a hundred feet high.
两幢大楼伫立在那里，稍大的那栋高达近百英尺。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>[用作系动词] 处于 (某种状态)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The house <strong>stood empty</strong> for a long time.
那所房子空了很长一段时间。</p></div></div>